put.description:
Updates the value and type of a deployment parameter.    Deployment parameters support a subset of the FME JSON Parameters specification.   Here are examples of JSON requests to define the types that are currently supported.

   **Text**
   ```
   {
     "value": "Example",
     "type": "text"
   }
   ```

   **Database Connection**
   ```
   {
     "value": "Example",
     "type": "dropdown",
     "choiceSettings": {
       "choiceSet": "dbConnections",
       "family": "Example"
     }
   }
   ```

   **Web Connection**
   ```
   {
     "value": "Example",
     "type": "dropdown",
     "choiceSettings": {
       "choiceSet": "webConnections",
       "services": [
         "Example"
       ],
       "excludedServices": [
         "Example"
       ]
     }
   }
   ```

post.description:
